INSERT INTO `news_description` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `news_id`, `language_id`) VALUES
(62, 'Our Company', '&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Embracing world class education is each and every Vietnamese student''s aspiration, be it a short summer program for intensive English studies, a high school degree, an undergraduate degree or a postgraduate degree. With a young population, of which approximately 3 million students entering high school and another roughly equivalent number of students graduating from high schools each year, a continuously increasing demand for studying abroad, resulted from dramatic economic growth over the past decades, Vietnam is and will have always been a very potential market for educational institutions around the world. With the will of helping Vietnamese students to succeed and catch that wave of overseas studying, Song Nguyen believes it possesses what it takes to be a good consultancy firm to deliver top quality advices and services to parents and students. Located in the south of Ho Chi Minh City in the new town of Phu My Hung, Song Nguyen offers a wide range of services that can fulfill every student and parent''s particular needs from selecting a school, arranging an accommodation, providing test preparation courses to visa preparation and air-ticket services. Song Nguyen has also teamed up with different partners around the world to assure that our students are well taken care of and that they can be assisted at anytime they need. The people at Song Nguyen, with their expertise and long-forged experience in the industry, have many connections with prestigious schools and educational institutions worldwide, are capable of providing personalized advices that suit the needs of every different students, and above all, have been themselves an overseas student, a parent, a teacher to understand the worries and concerns that parents and students are faced with. Finally, with a developing network of forty some institutions scattered through Asia, Oceania, Europe and the Americas, Song Nguyen is confident to represent hardworking Vietnamese students to the world, and bring the world''s education system closer to them, guaranteeing a better chance of success in their studying career.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;COMPANY DATA: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Company Full Name&lt;/strong&gt;: SONG NGUYEN OVERSEAS STUDYING COMPANY LIMITED&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Address: &lt;/strong&gt;R4-92 HUNG GIA II PHU MY HUNG, DISTRICT 7 HO CHI MINH CITY, VIETNAM&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Business License:&lt;/strong&gt; 0310852043&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Tel:&lt;/strong&gt; +84 8 5410 5770, +84 8 54105771&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Fax:&lt;/strong&gt; +84 8 5410 5772&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;E-mail:&lt;/strong&gt; info@sn.edu.vn&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Website:&lt;/strong&gt; www.sn.edu.vn&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BANKING INFORMATION:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Bank Name:&lt;/strong&gt; STANDARD CHARTERED BANK (VIETNAM) LIMITED&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Bank Address&lt;/strong&gt;: UNIT 101, SAIGON TRADE CENTER 37 TON DUC THANG, DISTRICT 1 HO CHI MINH CITY, VIETNAM&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Account name:&lt;/strong&gt; SONG NGUYEN OSC LTD&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Account number:&lt;/strong&gt; USD 99148596278&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Number of employees: 09&lt;br /&gt;\r\nContact person: BAO LAM – DEON / Mr. MANAGING DIRECTOR&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEmail: bao.lam@sn.edu.vn&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMobile: +84 90 808 1953&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 1),
(64, 'Our Core Values', '&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;SONG NGUYEN Co., Ltd is one of the leading overseas study consultancies in Vietnam. Our office is located in the centre of Phu My Hung, which is one of the most modern urban areas. Residents of this urban area are mostly wealthy families and have the high capacities to invest in their children’s education.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOur company is an official representative of student recruitment for international educational organizations, such as English-teaching schools, high schools, vocational training schools, colleges, universities and institutes in the US, Canada, the UK, Australia, New Zealand, Switzerland, Singapore… These schools and organizations are well-known and achieve the international standard. We always focus on the &lt;strong&gt;professionalism, enthusiasm&lt;/strong&gt;and &lt;strong&gt;work ethics&lt;/strong&gt;. SONG NGUYEN Co., Ltd with a young, dynamic, devoted and well-trained staff will provide students and their parents with the active support and the highest satisfaction. We always operate under the slogan: &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;“Dream wings fly away”&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;. When going to SONG NGUYEN Consultant Co., Ltd, students will certainly achieve two major goals of the life study: outstanding graduate student award from High school, college, university and success in their future career. These criteria are set out to represent our company name’s SONG NGUYEN and are also the dream of educators like us, the dream of students and their parents. The consultants of SONG NGUYEN are always educated and updated with the system and admission procedures as well as the visa process.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our mission:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTo bring world class education closer to the local Vietnamese students through superior services.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our vision:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTo be the most trusted educational consultancy in Ho Chi Minh City where parents and students would kindly recommend to their friends and families.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Our target:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTo give strong, continual supports to students and families from day one and turn every concern to reassured actions.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Our company aims to support:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Students who dream of being trained and educated abroad from high school to doctoral levels and plan to go back and help to built up a new Vietnam which is economically stronger, culturally richer and technologically developed.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Individuals and communities who are studying or working and would like to improve professional skills for daily life and vocational training.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 2, 1),
(66, 'Our Missions', '&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;The mission of SONG NGUYEN is to consult and support students with selecting majors suitable for their capacity and advise them on the best ways to achieve their education and career goals.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our services&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;A. CORE SERVICES:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Admission services, consultancy and provision of fundamental information about educational institutions (location, courses, tuitions and fees structures…) from various countries (The United States of America, Australia, New Zealand, The United Kingdom, Singapore, Canada, France, Switzerland…).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exchange programs for high school students.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Intensive summer English programs for secondary and high school students.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Conduction of tests preparation courses (TOEFL, IELTS, SAT, GRE…).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Conduction of soft-skills workshops to prepare psychologically and emotionally for students and parents.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;B. OTHER PREPARATIVE SERVICES:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Student visa service assistance.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Provision of necessary information and knowledge about the receiver country.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Financial evidence consultancy.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Money transfer (of tuitions, fees and other living costs, in compliance with Vietnamese banking regulations) assistance for students and parents.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Translation and notarization services.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air-ticket services&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Accommodation and Airport pick-up arrangements.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Family visit arrangements&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Seeking of invitation letters for scholars offered by Vietnamese Ministry of Education and Training&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 3, 1),
(68, 'Our Staffs', '&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;A. FOUNDER, ACADEMIC DIRECTOR:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Mr. Trieu Lam&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;- Bachelor of Mathematics, University of Education.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Master Degree in Education Management.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n-&amp;nbsp; 36 years being teacher of Mathematics.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n-&amp;nbsp; 32 years holding positions in managing education activities.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- In 1998, nominated as Vice-principal of Le Hong Phong High School for the Gifted - Ho Chi Minh City, in charge of the school''s discipline, extracurricular activities and foreign affairs.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- In latest Vice-principal position, having built good rapport and maintained broad relationships with key decision-makers from a large number of colleges and universities around the world.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Having recommended good and suitable foreign universities to a lot of gifted students, many of whom have gained outstanding accomplishments.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Ten-year experience being a consultant on both job-orientation and overseas studies to parents and students, especially 12th-grade students to select qualified overseas universities, the countries for their overseas studies and the future careers to choose.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;B. MANAGING DIRECTOR:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Mr. Bao Lam&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Bachelor of Commerce, Royal Melbourne Institute of Technology (‘RMIT’) University.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Senior Financial Consultant at Standard Chartered Bank (Vietnam) Limited, having built strong knowledge in banking industry and been familiarized with Vietnamese banking system and regulations.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Having attended summer programs and pursued high school education in the United States of America, thus having been equipped with countless of experiences as a student studying and living abroad.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;C. CO-FOUNDER, PARENTS RELATIONSHIP DIRECTOR:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ms. Hang Pham&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Bachelor of French, University of Education.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- &amp;nbsp;Ph.D Degree in Linguistic Science, Rouen University, France.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- 36 years being a teacher of French at various prestigious high schools, universities and foreign language centers.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Principal of Hong Chuyen Language and Education Center specializing in teaching Mathematics, Physics, Chemistry, Vietnamese Literature, Biology, English, French and Chinese for students from 8th grade to Senior years.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- In her last role at Le Hong Phong High School for the gifted as a French-Russian-Chinese Department Head, having organized many cultural exchange field trips to Europe and America for students and having built strong and long lasting relationships with major educational institutions in France, Belgium and Canada.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Having recommended countless numbers of students to study in prestigious universities in French-speaking countries, most of whom are now very successful at managerial level at multinational companies.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;D. STUDENT SERVICES COUNSELORS:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Bachelor of English&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Strong understandings of the industry, good knowledge of institutions’ information, service-oriented&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Continuously being trained to provide excellent services to parents and students.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 4, 1),
(70, 'Our Partners', '&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Song Nguyen&lt;/em&gt; has partnered up with various companies and individuals in the Americas, Australia, Singapore, France … for better taking care of the students during their time abroad. Our partners will assist us with airport pick up and accommodation/host families'' arrangements for the students, and in case of emergency, they will act on our behalf to solve the problems within 24 hours and help the students with anything they may need. Our commitment is to make studying abroad for Vietnamese students as exciting and enriching as possible, yet always maintain a safe and homey environment that gives parents a peace of mind.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Song Nguyen''&lt;/em&gt;s partners around the world are qualified and experienced organizations and/or individuals that will carry out our Intensive English Summers Programs, assuring that every student attending the program will have unforgettable time learning, self-developing, sight-seeing and having fun.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: nor