ows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Culinary arts:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;In this program, students learn the basics of food science, nutrition, and meal preparation right in WA’s own kitchen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Career computer technology:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;Virtually every career today requires computer skills. Course offerings include programming, tech support, desktop publishing and web design.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-left: 0.25in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Activities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;WashingtonAcademyis definitely a place where students can discover their talents, find like-minded friends, and be themselves. With over 50 clubs and activities, students at WA are hard-pressed to find something to do that doesn’t interest them. From the Fiber Arts Club to the Robotics Club, WA students do it all. Students at WA also create their own activities each year, from knitting to snowshoeing to archery. The experience of creating a club encourages leadership and individual growth while fostering communications with their peers. Most importantly – it’s a lot of fun.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-fami