x; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; The DeVry`s IT courses are among those of the 6 universities which the IT Directors in the US trust and where they send their staff to be educated (to Computer World Magazine).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; The&amp;nbsp; DeVry`s Master of Project Management course is one of the 17&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; American&amp;nbsp; universities’ courses&amp;nbsp; of this kind, recognized by PMI – the leading Project Management Experts Association in the world.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Devry accepts to transfer students who are studying in universities and colleges in Vietnam. The students can get 2/3 syllabus’s remission.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: st