(94, 'THE AMERICAN LANGUAGE AND CULTURE INSTITUTE CALIGORNIA STATE UNIVERSITY SAN MARCOS', '&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;The American Language and Culture Institute (ALCI) is the English language program at California State University San Marcos.&amp;nbsp; We offer many programs for international students and travelers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;The ALCI welcomes more than 100 students each year from countries including Brazil, China, Colombia, the Czech Republic, Denmark, Ecuador, El Salvador, Finland, Germany, Italy, Japan, Korea, Mali, Mexico, Saudi Arabia, Sweden, Switzerland, Taiwan,Thailand,&amp;nbsp;Turkey,Vietnam,andothers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nInstructors&amp;nbsp;in our Intensive Academic Preparation program have Master''s Degrees and several years of teaching experience.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Our average class size is 15 students. The average student age is 22 years old, but older students are welcome to join us.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;The ALCI is part of the California State University San Marcos campus, a modern, growing&amp;nbsp;university with the latest computer technology, high tech labs, athletic facilities, and state-of-the-art library facilities.&amp;nbsp; CSU San Marcos is a university dedicated to the academic success of global citizens.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ALCI Office&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe ALCI is located in Academic Hall, Room 111 on the CSU San Marcos campus.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ALCI Programs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.csusm.edu/alci/programs/academic_preparation.html&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Intensive Academic Preparation (IAP)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;The Intensive Academic Preparation (IAP) prepares you for study at an American university or college.&amp;nbsp;The IAP program&amp;nbsp;is also useful for professionals who need better skills and an advanced level of academic English.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCompletion of the IAP provides a&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.csusm.edu/alci/programs/toefl_waiver.html&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;TOEFL&amp;nbsp;Waiver&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;for graduate and undergraduate admission to California State University San Marcos (CSUSM).&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.csusm.edu/alci/applynow/conditional_admission.html&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;Conditional Admission&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to CSUSM is also available to qualified graduate and undergraduate students.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe IAP is a year-round program. Classes begin in the Fall, Spring, and Summer semesters. To enter this program, you must be at least 18 years old or a high-school graduate, and have basic English skills.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.csusm.edu/alci/programs/university_bridge.html&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summer University Bridge&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;The University Bridge program gives you a chance to learn and practice academic and cultural skills that can help you succeed at an American university.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Program Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; While attending the Bridge program, you:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; margin-left: 28.5pt;&quot;&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Research, write, docum